List of reccomendations are sent to users screen 
User is given the option to accept or decline 
While user declines item
	New item will be displayed in items place
If user accepts item 
	Send item to users shopping cart 
While user chooses to accept or decline items
	Wait for list of items to be complete
Send user to review page to see all items selected 
Give option to check out 
If user selects check out button 
	Send user to billing and shipping page 
If user is finished entering information for billing and shipping 
	Send user to confirmation screen
Ask user if they want text notifications for order
If user does not want text notifications 
	Send confirmation email to email on file 
If user does want text notification 
	Send confirmation to both email and number provided
Send user back to main screen